These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, montecristo
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | sprite |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Cigar     | chaman     | montecristo      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle
There 2 different types of food: lemon, pumpkin
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the person eating lemon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Pet      | turtle  | goldfish   |
| Food   | pumpkin | lemon  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
House: ranch-style, cottage
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, daffodil
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the cottage house is in an even position##4
2. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| House         | ranch-style   | cottage  |
| Flower   | daffodil | tulip  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

