.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different games are played: domino, poker
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Game          | domino | poker |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| Music-Genre     | hip-hop       | funk      |

