.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, reading
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| Hobby     | reading | camping |
| Flower   | bellflower | daffodil    |

 #################################

 
