.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, raspberry
2 different games are played: whist, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Food   | cauliflower     | raspberry     |
| Game           | snooker          | whist     |

